title: PLEASE NEED HELP :(
body:
please help me my nickname is Zedalize.   what is this ?
 "Your account is in the process of transferring. Please try again in a few minutes''

replies.body: This message indicates that your account is transferring to another region.  If this was not intended then it may be due to an unauthorized access.  Hit us up through an [account recovery form](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416) and our account team can stop it and help with restoring access.  Don't worry, we can help!

i transfer but it not didnt work and it gave me this message


Sorry for my bad english

Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new), and our account team will take a look.  It's possible that the process was stuck, but we can push it forward.  See you there!
